<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<text id="02-output-contract" title="Team Morale Pulse Survey Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="800" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema draft-07 for `MoralePulse` aggregate and alert event. Forbidden patterns + valid/invalid examples included.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/morale-pulse.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["team_id", "sprint_id", "week_iso", "responses_received", "team_size", "response_rate", "anonymity_threshold_met", "scores", "alerts_triggered"],
  "properties": {
    "team_id": {"type": "string"},
    "sprint_id": {"type": "string"},
    "week_iso": {"type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9]{4}-W[0-9]{2}$"},
    "responses_received": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 0},
    "team_size": {"type": "integer", "minimum": 3},
    "response_rate": {"type": "number", "minimum": 0, "maximum": 1},
    "anonymity_threshold_met": {"type": "boolean"},
    "scores": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["enps", "workload", "autonomy", "clarity"],
      "properties": {
        "enps": {"type": "object", "properties": {"value": {"type": "integer", "minimum": -100, "maximum": 100}, "promoter_pct": {"type": "number"}, "passive_pct": {"type": "number"}, "detractor_pct": {"type": "number"}}},
        "workload": {"type": "object", "properties": {"mean": {"type": "number"}, "median": {"type": "number"}}},
        "autonomy": {"type": "object", "properties": {"mean": {"type": "number"}, "median": {"type": "number"}}},
        "clarity": {"type": "object", "properties": {"mean": {"type": "number"}, "median": {"type": "number"}}}
      }
    },
    "alerts_triggered": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["alert_id", "trigger", "evidence", "action_required", "due_by", "responsible_pm"],
        "properties": {
          "alert_id": {"type": "string"},
          "trigger": {"enum": ["enps_drop", "axis_median_low", "response_rate_low"]},
          "evidence": {"type": "object"},
          "action_required": {"enum": ["one_on_ones_within_48h", "survey_pause"]},
          "due_by": {"type": "string", "format": "date-time"},
          "responsible_pm": {"type": "string"}
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>`scores.*.median` populated when `anonymity_threshold_met: false` — violates `r2-anonymity-floor`.</item>
      <item>`scores.enps.value` derived from arithmetic mean — violates `fm-06`; must be `%Promoters - %Detractors`.</item>
      <item>Comment-box text included anywhere in this object — comments are private to PM.</item>
      <item>5+ questions in survey — violates `r1-four-question-cap`.</item>
      <item>Alert with `due_by` &gt; 48 business hours from trigger — violates `r4-action-sla`.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "team_id": "checkout-squad", "sprint_id": "S14", "week_iso": "2026-W21",
  "responses_received": 5, "team_size": 6, "response_rate": 0.83,
  "anonymity_threshold_met": true,
  "scores": {
    "enps": {"value": -40, "promoter_pct": 20, "passive_pct": 20, "detractor_pct": 60},
    "workload": {"mean": 3.4, "median": 3},
    "autonomy": {"mean": 5.6, "median": 6},
    "clarity": {"mean": 4.2, "median": 4}
  },
  "alerts_triggered": [
    {"alert_id": "a-2026W21-1", "trigger": "axis_median_low", "evidence": {"axis": "workload", "median": 3},
     "action_required": "one_on_ones_within_48h", "due_by": "2026-05-25T17:00:00Z", "responsible_pm": "pm-handle"}
  ]
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "team_id": "x", "sprint_id": "S14", "week_iso": "2026-W21",
  "responses_received": 1, "team_size": 6, "response_rate": 0.16,
  "anonymity_threshold_met": false,
  "scores": {"enps": {"value": 4.5}, "workload": {"mean": 4, "median": 4}, "autonomy": {"mean": 5, "median": 5}, "clarity": {"mean": 6, "median": 6}},
  "alerts_triggered": []
}
]]></code>
    <note>N-of-1 with anonymity false but medians populated; eNPS value is an arithmetic mean (4.5) not integer NPS; no alert despite low response rate.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-team-morale-pulse-survey.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
